PrecisM.S.C. ELECTRONICS LIMITED REMISSION ORDER which provides for the remission, in an amount equal to the federal sales tax inventory rebate, of the tax paid by the aforementioned on certain new electronic goods in its inventory on January 1, 1991, that were imported on consignment before 1991 and subsequently sold, rented or leased to others in the ordinary course of their commercial activity.
